description: Cliff, the 21 year old stud on this page, is a laid-back guy who says he enjoys nothing more than to treating a beautiful woman to a night out on the town full of drinks and dreams. Works for us.This big jock is a bit shy, but once he gets comfortable, you can see he loves to show-off. He's proud of what he's got, and as you'll see, what he's working with definitely keeps his women satisfied and coming back for seconds.So join Cliff as he spends some quality time with himself. Because you know he's enjoying himself.Enjoy!
title: Cliff
